50
00:04:43,605 --> 00:04:44,845
Let's go.

51
00:04:50,165 --> 00:04:51,045
Gu Nanxi.

52
00:04:51,365 --> 00:04:52,605
-Yes?
-Class is starting.

53
00:04:52,805 --> 00:04:53,765
Yes, it's starting.

54
00:04:53,925 --> 00:04:54,805
It's starting.

55
00:05:12,525 --> 00:05:14,765
Most of you would have heard

56
00:05:15,205 --> 00:05:18,725
that the time for
Ming De College's excursion has come.

57
00:05:22,565 --> 00:05:23,405
Calm down!

58
00:05:24,765 --> 00:05:27,725
For this excursion,
we'll be going to Luzui cliff.

59
00:05:27,805 --> 00:05:30,205
It'll be a camping trip
for two days and one night.

60
00:05:30,445 --> 00:05:32,645
The trip is set for this weekend.

61
00:05:34,525 --> 00:05:36,925
Don't you have a music video shoot
this weekend?

62
00:05:38,725 --> 00:05:39,565
