75
00:06:35,645 --> 00:06:37,005
Hello, Daniel.

76
00:06:45,165 --> 00:06:46,005
Okay.

77
00:06:46,525 --> 00:06:47,365
I got it.

78
00:06:49,925 --> 00:06:50,765
Okay.

79
00:06:59,605 --> 00:07:01,365
That conversation was so short.

80
00:07:01,885 --> 00:07:05,365
I suppose his manager is really efficient.

81
00:07:10,885 --> 00:07:13,125
Hello, Daniel.

82
00:07:13,565 --> 00:07:14,725
What's up?

83
00:07:14,925 --> 00:07:16,165
Qingchen, here's the thing.

84
00:07:16,245 --> 00:07:19,285
Situ Feng has plans for this weekend.
He's going to his college's excursion.

85
00:07:19,365 --> 00:07:20,405
It's compulsory.

86
00:07:20,485 --> 00:07:22,805
There'll be last minute changes
for our music video shoot.

87
00:07:23,045 --> 00:07:24,525
Qingqing seems to be in a good mood.

88
00:07:24,885 --> 00:07:27,725
Why is she giggling?
who is she talking to?

89
00:07:27,805 --> 00:07:29,445
I see.

90
00:07:30,085 --> 00:07:31,245
That's too bad.

91
00:07:31,725 --> 00:07:33,525
I was all prepared for it.

92
00:07:34,445 --> 00:07:35,845
But don't worry.

93
00:07:36,085 --> 00:07:37,405
School is more important.

94
00:07:38,045 --> 00:07:39,285
No, it's not cancelled.

95
00:07:39,365 --> 00:07:40,805
We're just changing the location.

96
00:07:40,885 --> 00:07:42,685
They will be going to Luzui cliff

97
00:07:42,765 --> 00:07:46,085
so we'll shoot our music video there.
It was originally an outdoor shoot anyway.

98
00:07:46,165 --> 00:07:47,845
Camping will start right after
the shooting.

99
00:07:47,925 --> 00:07:49,445
We're killing two birds with one stone.

100
00:07:49,525 --> 00:07:51,485
