I hope you're okay with it.

101
00:07:52,045 --> 00:07:53,245
No.

102
00:07:54,125 --> 00:07:56,125
Don't worry, it won't affect you
that much.

103
00:07:56,205 --> 00:07:58,325
I'll send you the schedule later. Bye.

104
00:07:58,805 --> 00:08:01,125
Hello? I'm not finished yet. Hello?

105
00:08:01,205 --> 00:08:02,125
Hello?

106
00:08:05,805 --> 00:08:07,725
I wasn't even done yet.

107
00:08:10,565 --> 00:08:12,765
What's wrong with you?
Are you high on drugs?

108
00:08:13,925 --> 00:08:15,205
It's all because of you.

109
00:08:19,485 --> 00:08:20,525
Because of me?

110
00:08:27,485 --> 00:08:28,565
All right, you're dismissed.

111
00:08:29,165 --> 00:08:31,205
Hand in your 10,000-word report
by tomorrow.

112
00:08:41,645 --> 00:08:42,684
Ms. Chen.

113
00:08:42,765 --> 00:08:44,845
Yes? How can I help you?

114
00:08:46,725 --> 00:08:48,564
It's about the excursion this weekend.

115
00:08:48,645 --> 00:08:50,285
Can I apply for a leave of absence?

116
00:08:52,365 --> 00:08:53,525
Qingqing.

117
00:08:53,605 --> 00:08:57,285
This is a compulsory trip
for all students.

118
00:08:57,405 --> 00:08:59,365
We can't allow it.

119
00:08:59,645 --> 00:09:01,565
Even Situ Feng can't excuse himself.

120
00:09:01,805 --> 00:09:03,725
He has to come after his shoot ends.

121
00:09:04,845 --> 00:09:07,085
Then is it possible for me
to go there a bit late?

122
00:09:07,165 --> 00:09:09,805
I promise I won't be late
for the gathering, please?

123
00:09:10,845 --> 00:09:11,805
Pretty please?

124
00:09:12,045 --> 00:09:12,885
Can I?

125
00:09:12,965 --> 00:09:14,005
All right.

126
00:09:14,085 --> 00:09:15,725
Try to come as soon as possible.

127
00:09:26,285 --> 00:09:28,405
Am I hallucinating due to extreme hunger?

128
00:09:29,005 --> 00:09:30,485
The old witch is smiling now.

129
00:09:32,605 --> 00:09:35,565
I think I'm hungry too.

130
00:09:42,765 --> 00:09:45,245
LUZUI CLIFF

131
00:09:50,125 --> 00:09:52,165
Okay, cut! That's a wrap.

132
00:09:52,365 --> 00:09:54,005
-Thank you, director.
-Thank you, director.

133
00:09:54,085 --> 00:09:56,045
-Thank you, director.
-Thank you, director.

134
00:09:56,125 --> 00:09:58,845
